uteIdLanguageWritten":"ITALIAN","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Italian","commentText":"Unisciti a noi per un'esperienza unica e speciale dedicata a Twinkles con Peter Carnavas. Una mattinata all'insegna del canto, della lettura e di tutto ciò che riguarda \"Blue Whale Blues\" nella Galleria."},{"marketVariantId":"Korean","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"KOREAN","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Korean","commentText":"피터 카나바스와 함께하는 아주 특별한 트윙클스 행사에 여러분을 초대합니다. 갤러리에서 노래도 부르고 책도 읽고, '블루 웨일 블루스'에 관한 모든 것을 즐기는 시간을 보내세요."},{"marketVariantId":"Chinese Traditional","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"CHINESE-T","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Chinese Traditional","commentText":"來參加由彼得·卡納瓦斯帶來的特別版「閃爍」體驗活動吧！在畫廊裡，我們將度過一個充滿歌唱、朗讀和所有與“藍鯨藍調”相關內容的上午。"},{"marketVariantId":"French","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"FRENCH","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"French","commentText":"Venez vivre une expérience unique et exceptionnelle avec Peter Carnavas et Twinkles. Au programme : une matinée de chansons, de lectures et de découvertes autour de l’univers de « Blue Whale Blues » à la galerie."},{"marketVariantId":"Japanese","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"JAPANESE","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Japanese","commentText":"ピーター・カルナバスと一緒に、特別なトゥインクルズのイベントに参加しませんか？ギャラリーで歌を歌ったり、読み聞かせをしたり、ブルーホエール・ブルースにまつわるあらゆることを楽しめる午前中をお過ごしください。"},{"marketVariantId":"Chinese Simplified","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"CHINESE-S","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Chinese Simplified","commentText":"来参加由彼得·卡纳瓦斯带来的特别版“闪烁”体验活动吧！在画廊里，我们将度过一个充满歌唱、朗读和所有与“蓝鲸蓝调”相关内容的上午。"},{"marketVariantId":"Spanish","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"SPAN-EUR","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Spanish","commentText":"Acompáñanos en una experiencia única e irrepetible de Twinkles con Peter Carnavas. Una mañana llena de canciones, lecturas y todo lo relacionado con \"Blue Whale Blues\" en la galería."},{"marketVariantId":"German","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"GERMAN","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"German","commentText":"Erleben Sie mit Peter Carnavas ein ganz besonderes Twinkles-Event. Ein Vormittag voller Lieder, Lesungen und allem rund um das Thema „Blue Whale Blues“ in der Galerie."}],"productSite":[{"siteName":"The Write Gallery","attributeIdSiteType":"VENUE","attributeIdSiteTypeDescription":"Venue","productSiteAddressRelationship":[{"attributeIdAddress":"PHYSICAL","attributeIdAddressDescription":"Physical","addressLine1":"126 Margaret Street","addressLine2":"","suburbName":"","cityName":"Toowoomba City","areaName":"","stateName":"Queensland","countryName":"Australia","addressPostalCode":"4350","overrideDomesticRegionFlag":"0","geocodeGdaLatitude":"-27.5618348","geocodeGdaLongitude":"151.9571905","productSiteAddressStreetDirectoryRelationship":""}],"productSiteAttributeRelationship":"","productSiteCommentRelationship":"","productSiteCommunicationRelationship":"","productSiteLicenceRelationship":"","productSiteRelatedSiteRelationship":"","productSiteMultimediaRelationship":"","productSiteContactRelationship":""}],"